JOHANNESBURG - One of the most interesting bouts on the forthcoming EFC 72 event features the debutante Paulwethu Numba against one of the most recognisable faces of African Women's MMA, Shana Power (2-1). Power returns to the Hexagon after an absence of a year-and-a-half. READ: The Clinch Predix: EFC 68 Muyambo vs Roets Simon Stephens spoke to a variety of EFC stars and staff to find out their thoughts on 'Titanium's welcomed resurgence. The fight will take place in Cape Town on Agust 11. eNCA